OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1777295491
OL,3,CHMS Victory masts to be removed as
OL,4,Cpart of #42 million conservation
OL,5,Cproject
OL,7,FA scaffolding structure will enclose
OL,8,Fthe ship, which will remain in place
OL,9,Funtil the conservation work is
OL,10,Fcompleted in 2033.
OL,12,FAndrew Baines, executive director of
OL,13,Fmuseum operations for National Museum
OL,14,Fof the Royal Navy, described it as a
OL,15,F"key moment" in the project.
OL,17,F"Our team has planned this step in
OL,18,Fmeticulous detail, but we still have
OL,19,Fto work around factors like the
OL,20,Fweather," he said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1777295491
OL,3,CHMS Victory masts to be removed as
OL,4,Cpart of #42 million conservation
OL,5,Cproject
OL,7,F"That's why we will carry out the
OL,8,Flifts overnight, so we can work safely
OL,9,Fand without interruption for several
OL,10,Fhours at a time."
OL,12,FHe added: "The operation itself will
OL,13,Fbe impressive with a 750-tonne crane
OL,14,Frigged on site for a week.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1777295491
OL,3,CHMS Victory masts to be removed as
OL,4,Cpart of #42 million conservation
OL,5,Cproject
OL,7,F"We have learned a huge amount from
OL,8,Fthe removal of main lower mast in 2021
OL,9,Fand once all masts are removed and
OL,10,Fsafely stored, we can begin the
OL,11,Fcritical work of conserving them
OL,12,Fbefore their eventual return to the
OL,13,Fship in 2033."
OL,15,FStuart Sheldon, NMRN lead rigger,
OL,16,Fsaid: "HMS Victory matters to people
OL,17,Fin a way few objects do. That brings
OL,18,Freal pressure, and it should.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1777295491
OL,3,CHMS Victory masts to be removed as
OL,4,Cpart of #42 million conservation
OL,5,Cproject
OL,7,F"This lift is complex and it needs
OL,8,Fabsolute precision. Putting the plan
OL,9,Finto action on the night will be a
OL,10,Fcareer highlight for the whole team."
OL,12,FHMS Victory, which is the world's
OL,13,Foldest commissioned warship, was
OL,14,Ffamously Nelson's flagship at the
OL,15,FBattle of Trafalgar, and it was on the
OL,16,Fship's quarterdeck that he was fatally
OL,17,Fshot by a French sniper on October 21,
OL,18,F1805.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
